## 9. Matchlock Integration Strategy

### Option 1: Direct Dependency (Recommended)

Add Matchlock as a Go module dependency:

```go
// go.mod
require github.com/jingkaihe/matchlock v0.x.x
```

Benefits:
- Upstream updates automatically available
- No maintenance burden
- Community support

### Option 2: Vendor with Modifications

If Matchlock needs modifications:
1. Fork to `github.com/unstablebuild/matchlock`
2. Apply necessary patches
3. Maintain as an internal fork

### Option 3: Interface Abstraction

Create an interface that Matchlock implements, allowing future replacement:

```go
// api/sandboxapi/vmruntime/runtime.go

package vmruntime

type VMRuntime interface {
    CreateVM(config VMConfig) (VM, error)
    // ...
}

// Matchlock implementation
type matchlockRuntime struct {
    // Wraps matchlock
}
```

